{"id": 1733, "genre": 1001, "title": "现如今你都有哪些久违的安静时刻?", "description": "从一个屏幕到另一个屏幕，睡觉前最后一刻也在和手机作伴，所以你都在什么时候抽空松弛一下？", "record_count": 3364, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20170608161611hLE0rKzdYDZtfRWg.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 2, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-06-10T17:00:02Z", "options": [{"id": 211712, "content": "在图书馆偶遇一本喜欢的书，不知不觉读到闭馆铃响", "image": null, "praise_count": 18, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 777780}, {"id": 211968, "content": "游泳，很适合冥想。没有任何屏幕。", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 519738}, {"id": 212224, "content": "把手机关掉的一天", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1046491}, {"id": 212480, "content": "做完一个加班狗，在周末早上早起早读的时候。家人未醒，可以慢节奏。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053720}, {"id": 211713, "content": "比赛结束后独自去后台换衣服的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1043547}, {"id": 211969, "content": "洗澡和做饭的时候  因为没有办法用手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 843642}, {"id": 212225, "content": "破罐子破摔的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 907285}, {"id": 213249, "content": "对事物有感触或听到令自己有感触的音乐的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 938832}, {"id": 211714, "content": "一边做菜，一边听音乐的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 313814}, {"id": 211970, "content": "看儿子努力学习打篮球，想起自己", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052775}, {"id": 211715, "content": "上下班的路上。周末从商场回家的路上。", "image": null, "praise_count": 9, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1041393}, {"id": 212227, "content": "晚上两点以后", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 456508}, {"id": 211716, "content": "看书、弹吉他、跑步", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 925783}, {"id": 211972, "content": "晨跑的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 970684}, {"id": 211717, "content": "坐车发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 238, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 661570}, {"id": 211973, "content": "回忆过去", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052781}, {"id": 212229, "content": "睡前的胡思乱想，没有手机", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053173}, {"id": 212485, "content": "答辩完", "image": "img/option/option/20170612204945hswxaPmLDbBnXvOq", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 719357}, {"id": 227589, "content": "练字带着耳机，耳边充斥着歌声的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1097434}, {"id": 211718, "content": "冥想的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 746714}, {"id": 211974, "content": "看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1034969}, {"id": 212230, "content": "期末考作弊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 116772}, {"id": 212486, "content": "写作业", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1005156}, {"id": 214022, "content": "刚忙完回到家的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1057700}, {"id": 211719, "content": "女朋友吻我的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 11, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 932914}, {"id": 211975, "content": "骑单车", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1247392}, {"id": 212231, "content": "早上醒的很早不愿意看手机的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1018916}, {"id": 212487, "content": "手机关机后。。。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 960025}, {"id": 214279, "content": "现在", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1058389}, {"id": 211720, "content": "一个人上自习", "image": null, "praise_count": 7, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 890342}, {"id": 211976, "content": "散步回家路上，戴着耳机享受音乐。", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 138151}, {"id": 212232, "content": "思念一个人的深夜", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1010976}, {"id": 212488, "content": "健身房跑步的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053745}, {"id": 214024, "content": "在江心的一叶孤舟上钓鱼，仅能听到水浪拍打船壁和偶尔飞过头顶的大鸟凄鸣的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051505}, {"id": 222216, "content": "谁也不在，一边嗑瓜子一边看书", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1079111}, {"id": 211721, "content": "把手机放在大衣柜顶上，够不下来，就算了的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1029890}, {"id": 211977, "content": "雨后夜晚，坐在公交车后排，望向车窗外黑夜中灯光阑珊城市之时，世界的干净且安静的。", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052782}, {"id": 212233, "content": "坐的地铁那届车厢只有我一个人的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 4, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 790711}, {"id": 211722, "content": "泡杯茶，打开书，安安静静的时刻", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1045254}, {"id": 211978, "content": "和喜欢的姑娘聊天的", "image": null, "praise_count": 5, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 981317}, {"id": 212234, "content": "做火车，看着窗外发呆", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 921540}, {"id": 211723, "content": "在没人的教室复习", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052435}, {"id": 211979, "content": "学校每晚十一点断网关灯以后，清晨室友在睡懒觉的时候。", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1037864}, {"id": 212491, "content": "喝茶?写字的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1053772}, {"id": 211724, "content": "夜幕降临的时候，坐在公交车最后，听着歌，看这个城市的灯火阑珊", "image": null, "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1051976}, {"id": 211980, "content": "看书是很安静，就是现在安静不下来去看书，好矛盾", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1052067}, {"id": 212236, "content": "晚上健身的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 624350}, {"id": 213004, "content": "大概是……几张空白的卷子摆在你面前 你都不知道老师在讲啥 然后这个时候老班走了过来?(⁎⚈᷀᷁ᴗ⚈᷀᷁⁎)还特意观察了一下你的卷子和其他同学的卷子是否一致", "image": "img/option/option/20170614213352S5sAWovl9rd3JmEg", "praise_count": 1, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1055373}, {"id": 211981, "content": "考试收刀入鞘的时候", "image": null, "praise_count": 3, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 825428}, {"id": 212237, "content": "一口气通关一个游戏", "image": null, "praise_count": 2, "perfect": 0, "select": 0, "author": 1221934}]}